TextEng: So you think if Morag awakes she'll turn the North into a tropical jungle?
Text: 그러니까 모라그가 깨어나면 북부를 열대 정글로 바꿀 거라고?

TextEng: Morag make winter go away? She got big magic!
Text: 모라그가 겨울 없애? 큰 마법 가졌어!

TextEng: Morag was foolish to trust her fate to a group of slaves.
Text: 모라그도 자기 운명을 노예 무리에게 맡기다니 어리석었군.

TextEng: Morag be stupid, hoping slaves wake her up!
Text: 모라그 바보야, 노예들이 깨워줄 거라고 생각하다니!

TextEng: How did Maugrim become involved in all this?
Text: 모그림은 어떻게 이 일에 관여하게 됐지?

TextEng: How Maugrim get in this stuff?
Why would she imprison herself inside this Source Stone?
Text: 왜 자기 자신을 이 근원석 안에 가둔 거지?

TextEng: Why Morag go inside stone?
But the Words of Power are safe here in Castle Never!
Text: 하지만 권능의 언령은 네버 성에서 안전하잖아!

TextEng: What are you doing in this prison?
Text: 이 감옥에서 뭘 하고 있는 거야?

TextEng: Who are you again?
Morag? Source Stone? Old Ones? I'm lost.
Text: 모라그? 근원석? 태고의 존재? 무슨 말인지 모르겠어.

TextEng: Sorry, I can't help you with this.
But Power Words be safe in castle!
Why you in this jail?
Who you be?
Morag? Old Ones? Source Stone? Me lost.
Text: 모라그? 태고 존재? 근원석? 나 모르겠어.

TextEng: Sorry. Me not help you with this.
What must I do?
What me need do?
I will return once I have the final Word of Power!
Me be back when me got last Power Word.
How do I know I can trust you?
Me not trust lizard girly.
I want to ask you some questions.
Me want ask you stuff.
Tell me about Maugrim.
Tell me about Aribeth.
Tell me about you.
Tell me about Morag and the Old Ones.
Tell me about the Words of Power and the Source Stone.
Me want know stuff 'bout Maugrim.
Me want know stuff 'bout Aribeth.
Me want know stuff 'bout you.
Me want know stuff 'bout Morag and Oldies.
Text: 나 모라그랑 옛날 존재 얘기 듣고 싶어.

TextEng: Me want know stuff 'bout Power Words and Source Stone.
Text: 나 언령이랑 근원석 얘기 듣고 싶어.

TextEng: Then all is lost!
Surely there must be something we can do.
Text: 분명 뭔가 할 수 있는 게 있을 거야.

TextEng: I knew I couldn't trust you!
Text: 널 믿으면 안 된다는 걸 알았어!

TextEng: You mean we is going to lose?
Me not give up! Me got do something!
Text: 나 포기 안 해! 뭔가 해야 해!

TextEng: Me know me not trust you, lizard girly!
Text: 나 알았어 널 믿으면 안 된다고, 도마뱀 여자!

TextEng: I will enter the Source Stone and destroy Morag!
How can I enter the Source Stone?
I'm not going to do this!
Where are the Words of Power now?
Me go into Source Stone and kill Morag!
How me get inside Source Stone?
Me not want do this!
Where be Power Words now?
What does this have to do with me?
What this got do with me?
Me got Word of Power number four right here!
Text: 나 네 번째 언령 여기 갖고 있어!

TextEng: I have the fourth Word of Power right here!
Text: 네 번째 권능의 언령이 여기 있어!
